---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service | Apex Web Solutions"
  description="Read the Terms of Service for Apex Web Solutions. Understand the agreement, intellectual property rights, and conditions for using our services."
>
  <div class="bg-background min-h-screen pt-24 pb-12">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4">
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-4xl font-bold">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8 text-sm">
        Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing and using the website of Apex Web Solutions, you accept
          and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">2. Services</h2>
        <p>
          Apex Web Solutions provides web design, development, and hosting
          services. We reserve the right to withdraw or amend the services we
          provide without notice.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          The content, layout, design, data, databases, and graphics on this
          website are protected by intellectual property laws. Unless expressly
          permitted, you may not copy, distribute, or display any part of this
          website.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">4. Payment Terms</h2>
        <p>
          Payment terms for our services will be outlined in your specific
          project proposal or agreement. Standard terms generally require a
          deposit before work commences.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          In no event shall Apex Web Solutions be liable for any indirect,
          incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of
          your use of our services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">6. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the
          laws of South Africa.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">7. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to update these Terms of Service at any time. We
          will notify you of any changes by posting the new Terms on this page.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium">
          Email: <a
            href="mailto:info@apexwebsolutions.co.za"
            class="text-primary hover:underline">info@apexwebsolutions.co.za</a
          >
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
